  ('Tall kneeling', 'trainerize', '17554859', TRUE, '{}', NULL, '{}', '{}', '{"Trainerize: Strength"}', NULL, '{}', '1. Tall kneeling hold — fingertips on bench · 3 × 5 sec
Kneel upright on thick mat, hips over knees. Squeeze glutes, tall spine. Monitor knee comfort — never force. This alone is the exercise on difficult days.

2. Tall kneeling — no hands · 3 × 10 sec
Hands to chest. Progress to eyes closed when steady. 

3. Tall kneeling weight shift · 8 reps
Slowly shift weight left to right. Don''t let hips drop. Mimics lateral instability of water. One hand available if needed.', NULL, 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Mzvc9Dompvc/mqdefault.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mzvc9Dompvc'),
